        "TileImage": "$($repository 859addff-9450-468a-8939-1be471077573).Image",
        "Description": "Good Morning, 47.\rCelebrations for New Year&#39;s Eve at The Sceptre have already begun! We have also found traces of espionage in the building, more specifically, three spies undercover as guards. Their goal is to get as much information as possible about Omar Al-Ghazali for blackmail. We cannot let his holidays get ruined with costly bribes! Show them that only YOU are allowed to ruin somebody&#39;s holiday!\rGood luck, 47.\r\rBy bgyorok\r&lt;HCCE&gt;",
